    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Asplenium mohillense are fever, often caused by its antipyretic properties that help reduce body temperature. Inflammation is another condition that can be alleviated with this plant, due to the presence of flavonoids that exhibit anti-inflammatory activity. Asplenium mohillense has also been used to treat respiratory issues, such as bronchitis, by providing expectorant properties that facilitate mucus expulsion from the lungs. Its antimicrobial properties also make it effective in treating skin infections, including acne, by eliminating bacteria that cause these conditions. Furthermore, Asplenium mohillense has been found to exhibit antioxidant properties, which can help mitigate the effects of oxidative stress and reduce the risk of cardiovascular disease.",
